      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Write record [idv] normalizzato             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-idv-000      thru wrt-rec-idv-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
